    <item>
      <title>硅谷银行破产计划获批，但 20 亿美元 FDIC 纠纷仍未解决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/svb-ends-bankruptcy-but-dealt-a-setback-in-2-billion-fdic-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名法官批准了硅谷银行金融集团的重组协议，但却使该公司在与联邦监管机构的斗争中遭遇挫折，该斗争旨在收回去年硅谷银行子公司倒闭时所持有的约 20 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/svb-ends-bankruptcy-but-dealt-a-setback-in-2-billion-fdic-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 15:16:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>私募股权失败导致投资者面临抛售风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/private-equity-drought-has-made-investors-more-reliant-on-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近年来私募股权回报率的下滑，迫使美国养老金和捐赠基金转向一种古老而熟悉的投资：股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/private-equity-drought-has-made-investors-more-reliant-on-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 08:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>信贷恐慌指数大幅下跌，迫使企业借款人退避三舍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/asia-high-grade-dollar-bond-spreads-widen-the-most-in-22-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，全球主要信用风险指标飙升，因人们对经济增长放缓的担忧日益加剧。这场动荡实际上导致美国公司债券销售停滞，而这原本是一年中最繁忙的日子之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/asia-high-grade-dollar-bond-spreads-widen-the-most-in-22-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:22:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳斯达克 100 指数本月开局表现创 2008 年以来最差：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对世界最大经济体增长放缓的担忧引发人们警告称，今年的股市涨势已过度，新一轮波动席卷了整个市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
